OL,3,CJK Rowling says 'arrest me' in
OL,4,Cchallenge to Scotland's new hate crime
OL,5,Claws
OL,7,FThe legislation consolidates existing
OL,8,Fhate crime laws and creates a new
OL,9,Foffence of stirring up hatred against
OL,10,Fprotected characteristics
OL,12,FJK Rowling has challenged the Scottish
OL,13,FGovernment's controversial new
OL,14,Fclaiming the legislation is "wide open
OL,15,Fto abuse."
OL,17,FThe Harry Potter author, who has
OL,18,Fbecome a fierce critic of the Scottish
OL,19,FGovernment's stance on transgender
OL,20,Frights, has been one of the highest
OL,21,Fprofile critics of the legislation.
