OL,4,Cchallenge to Scotland's new hate crime
OL,5,Claws
OL,7,FThe Hate Crime and Public Order
OL,8,F(Scotland) Act was passed by MSPs in
OL,9,F2021, consolidating existing hate
OL,10,Fcrime legislation and creating a new
OL,11,Foffence of stirring up hatred against
OL,12,Fprotected characteristics, although
OL,13,Fsex has been omitted in favour of a
OL,14,Fstandalone Bill designed to tackle
OL,15,Fmisogyny.
OL,17,FA stirring up offence on the basis of
OL,18,Frace has been on the statute book in
OL,19,FScotland since 1986.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G2/17
