OL,7,FBut the legislation has raised
OL,8,Fconcerns about a potential chilling of
OL,9,Ffree speech.
OL,11,FHowever, women have not been given
OL,12,Fprotection under the law, with the
OL,13,FScottish Government instead promising
OL,14,Fto bring forward legislation to tackle
OL,15,Fmisogyny.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G3/17
