OL,7,FBut with the new Act giving protection
OL,8,Fto transgender people, Rowling, who
OL,9,Fdoes not believe people can change
OL,10,Ftheir gender, insisted: "Freedom of
OL,11,Fspeech and belief are at an end in
OL,12,FScotland if the accurate description
OL,13,Fof biological sex is deemed criminal."
