OL,8,Fthe country, but if what I've written
OL,9,Fhere qualifies as an offence under the
OL,10,Fterms of the new act, I look forward
OL,11,Fto being arrested when I return to the
OL,12,Fbirthplace of the Scottish
OL,13,FEnlightenment."
OL,15,FOther critics include podcaster Joe
