OL,5,Claws
OL,7,FThe Act has also raised the ire of
OL,8,Fpolicing bodies, with the Scottish
OL,9,FPolice Federation (SPF) claiming
OL,10,Ftraining for officers is not enough
OL,11,Fand the Association of Scottish Police
OL,12,FSuperintendents (ASPS) raising
OL,13,Fconcerns about the legislation being
OL,14,Fweaponised for political purposes.
OL,16,FASPS warned vexatious complaints could
OL,17,Fbe made against people based on their
OL,18,Fviews by political opponents.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G7/17
