OL,5,Claws
OL,7,FIn a letter to Holyrood's Justice
OL,8,FCommittee, they said the law could be
OL,9,F"weaponised" by an "activist fringe"
OL,10,Facross the political spectrum.
OL,12,FBut on Friday, First Minister Humza
OL,13,FYousaf said: "I would say to anybody
OL,14,Fwho thinks they are a victim of
OL,15,Fhatred, we take that seriously, if you
OL,16,Ffelt you are a victim of hatred, then
OL,17,Fof course reporting that to police is
OL,18,Fthe right thing to do.
