OL,7,FThis includes an explicit clause, a
OL,8,Fdefence for the accused's behaviour
OL,9,Fbeing "reasonable" and that the Act is
OL,10,Fcompatible with the European
OL,11,FConvention on Human Rights.
OL,13,FMr Yousaf also told journalists on
OL,14,FFriday that the legislation would not
OL,15,Fgo the way of other high-profile
OL,16,Flegislative U-turns under the SNP,
OL,17,Fsuch as the named persons scheme and
OL,18,Fthe Offensive Behaviour at Football
OL,19,FAct.
