OL,5,Claws
OL,7,FThe legislation, which he shepherded
OL,8,Fthrough Holyrood as former first
OL,9,Fminister Nicola Sturgeon's justice
OL,10,Fsecretary, "got the right balance"
OL,11,Fbetween protections against hate crime
OL,12,Fand freedom of speech, he said.
OL,14,F"Ultimately, once the Act comes into
OL,15,Fforce, I think it will do exactly what
OL,16,Fwe expect it to do, which is protect
OL,17,Fthe most marginalised in our
OL,18,Fcommunity," he added.
