OL,4,Cchallenge to Scotland's new hate crime
OL,5,Claws
OL,7,FThe Act has been a running sore for
OL,8,Fthe SNP-led government in recent
OL,9,Fyears, with a number of changes having
OL,10,Fto be made before it was passed and
OL,11,Fthe three-year gap before it came into
OL,12,Feffect.
OL,14,FBut critics, many of whom, including
OL,15,Fthe Harry Potter author, hold gender
OL,16,Fcritical views, have said it would be
OL,17,Fweaponised against them.
OL,19,FSNP MP Joanna Cherry has previously
OL,20,Fsaid being under police investigation
OL,21,Fcould be a punishment in itself.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G12/17
