OL,5,Claws
OL,7,FScottish Tory justice spokesman
OL,8,FRussell Findlay ` who along with his
OL,9,Fparty has been an ardent opponent of
OL,10,Fthe law ` said: "Officers would rather
OL,11,Ftackle real crimes and keep
OL,12,Fcommunities safe, rather than having
OL,13,Fto investigate malicious and spurious
OL,14,Fcomplaints.
OL,16,F"Humza Yousaf should bin his Hate
OL,17,FCrime Act and instead divert resources
OL,18,Ftowards frontline policing which is at
OL,19,Fbreaking point."
