OL,7,FBut Police Scotland Chief Constable Jo
OL,8,FFarrell, speaking at a meeting of the
OL,9,FScottish Police Authority board, said
OL,10,Fthe force would apply the Act "in a
OL,11,Fmeasured way".
OL,13,FShe added that there would be "close
OL,14,Fscrutiny" of how the legislation is
OL,15,Fbeing enforced as well as what reports
OL,16,Fare being received.
