OL,3,CJK Rowling says 'arrest me' in
OL,4,Cchallenge to Scotland's new hate crime
OL,5,Claws
OL,7,FThe law coming into force comes as
OL,8,FTory MSP Murdo Fraser revealed Police
OL,9,FScotland had recorded a non-crime hate
OL,10,Fincident in relation to a social media
OL,11,Fpost he made last year.
OL,13,FMr Fraser, in a letter last week,
OL,14,Furged the force to delete the file `
OL,15,Fwhich is recorded when an incident
OL,16,Fdoes not meet the hate crime threshold
OL,17,F` and did not rule out legal action if
OL,18,Fhis request was refused.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G15/17
