OL,5,Claws
OL,7,FMr Findlay described Mr Fraser's case
OL,8,Fas "sinister and unacceptable",
OL,9,Fraising concerns "innocent people will
OL,10,Fend up in secret police files".
OL,12,FThe recording of non-crime hate
OL,13,Fincidents, however, is not a feature
OL,14,Fof the legislation which came into
OL,15,Feffect on Monday, although an increase
OL,16,Fin reports as a result of the Act
OL,17,Fcould see more such incidents logged.
